======================================================================
Part 2: Growth rate I(x+1)/I(x) for large x
======================================================================

For a single brick K_c: I(x) = 1 + cx
  I(x+1)/I(x) = (1+c(x+1))/(1+cx) = 1 + c/(1+cx) → 1 as x → ∞

For simplex packing (1+x)^m: I(x+1)/I(x) = ((2+x)/(1+x))^m → 1 as x → ∞

But the USER said k-nacci → 2 and weighted → 3.
This suggests DIFFERENT limiting behavior...

